ions, and may","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"have submenus associated with them. Both items and sections usually","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"have some representation data, such as labels or icons. The type of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the associated action (ie whether it is stateful, and what kind of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"state it has) can influence the representation of the item."}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusMenuModelRef/ObjectProtocol-Implementations":{"type":"topic","kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusMenuModelRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusmenumodelref\/objectprotocol-implementations","title":"ObjectProtocol Implementations","abstract":[]}}}